item.title: More thoughts about music
item.description: The first result for it’s not the band I hate, it’s their fans on Ecosia leads to an old article from the GigCity website 1 about an upcoming Sloan show. I am thinking about Sloan because I am using their song Coax Me to test out several equalizer applications on my Mac and I am using the studio and live versions of Coax Me to test the software out.
